{
  "stem": "2723.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I have a vivid recollection that probably has nothing to do with anything, but it's part of my bizarre memories.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When one part of the people were being taken to the trains, a friend of my grandmother's-- an old lady-- saw me and called out to me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was the wife of the Rosh Hakol of the orthodoxy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Her fa-- Her husband was no longer alive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She was there on her own.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she wore a Tyrolean hat with a long feather-- a quail feather.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She wore hiking boots like you used to wear, thick socks, a leather skirt, and she had a cane with the metal symbols of achieved walks.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I can see this woman entering the train, tally hoing to me and saying, we'll meet over there, and sort of trying to reassure herself by reassuring us.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I thought of all bizarre sights, that probably carried the cake.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's probably what it was because I remember I was very conscious of having missed out on birthday and Rosh Hashanah and all the rest of it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By-- I was really itchy to get a-- away from there, because I realized my mother was here, but she isn't anymore.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I now want to go where she probably is waiting.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a-- a [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] roll call one day, and a very senior dignitary came, once again, to check who was there and who was going and who possibly could be bribed by-- or, who could bribe them to stay back.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he walked through the rows of people and-- and we had to stand very straight.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when he came to me, he looked me straight in the eyes and said, 'You are not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
